org.hps.recon.tracking.kalman

Class KalmanTrackFit2

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.recon.tracking.kalman.KalmanTrackFit2

  • class KalmanTrackFit2
extends Object
    Driver program for executing a Kalman refit of existing tracks. This version starts at layer N, filters to layer 0, then starts over using the fit result to start filtering from layer 0 outward. Then it smooths back to layer 0. The code assumes that the SiModules hold all the hits to be fit and only those hits. No pattern recognition is done; no hits are dropped.
